                    <h1 class="txt-black">Entry Dates</h1>
                        <p>Hosted for the first time on Thursday 26th of June 2014, The Maverick Awards for South African Youth Entrepreneurship Excellence represented South Africa's first award ceremony held to honour the excellence of young entrepreneurs across the country. Till today The Maverick Awards are South Africa's only youth entrepreneurship excellence awards.</p>
                        <p>Entries will be open for a 4 week period, starting on Monday 2nd March 2015 and closing on Friday 27th March 2015. Shortlisted finalists will be announced on Friday 1st May 2015 and winners will be announced at The Maverick Awards Gala Dinner on Friday 5th June 2015.</p>
